These are Puzzles for 4x7 Level 8

.:: Puzzle 4x7-Level-8-1::.
There are 7 different favourite beverages: 7up, cola, fanta, hot-chocolate, milk, soy-milk, tea
The people have 7 different jobs:  chef, dancer, manager, mechanic, musician, security-guard, social-worker
House: wooden, palace, cape-cod, ranch-style, cottage, art-deco, victorian
The people perfer 7 different movie-genres: western, sports, scientific, adventure, musical, action, time-travel
 1. the palace house is somewhere to the right of the wooden house##5
 2. the person drinking cola is somewhere to the left of the wooden house##5
 3. the dancer is somewhere to the left of the art-deco house##5
 4. the mechanic is on the left or right of the wooden house##3
 5. the manager is not to the left of the person watching scientific movies##8
 6. the social-worker is on the left or right of the person drinking soy-milk##3
 7. the dancer is not to the left of the person drinking cola##8
 8. the ranch-style house is not to the left of the person drinking cola##8
 9. the mechanic is not to the left of the person watching western movies##8
10. the person drinking fanta is somewhere between the manager and the person watching western movies##7
11. the person drinking cola is not to the left of the mechanic##8
12. the person drinking cola is somewhere to the left of the musician##5
13. the person watching scientific movies is not to the left of the cottage house##8
14. the person drinking milk is not the person watching western movies##6
15. the person drinking fanta is somewhere to the right of the palace house##5
16. the person drinking 7up is not to the left of the wooden house##8
17. the person drinking milk is not to the right of the person watching scientific movies##8
18. the person drinking soy-milk is on the left or right of the person watching sports movies##3
19. the person drinking cola is not to the left of the person watching western movies##8
20. the cottage house is somewhere to the left of the person watching adventure movies##5
21. the person watching sports movies is on the left of the art-deco house##1
22. the person watching western movies is not to the right of the person drinking soy-milk##8
23. the person drinking 7up is the cottage house##1
24. the person drinking soy-milk is somewhere to the left of the manager##5
25. the person watching action movies is not to the left of the mechanic##8
26. the palace house is somewhere to the left of the social-worker##5
27. the victorian house is somewhere to the right of the security-guard##5
28. the victorian house is somewhere between the palace house and the manager##7
29. the dancer is on the right of the mechanic##1
30. the person watching scientific movies is the person drinking soy-milk##1
31. the wooden house is on the left or right of the musician##3
32. the person drinking tea is on the left or right of the cottage house##3
33. the person drinking tea is not to the left of the person watching time-travel movies##8
34. the person drinking milk is not the person watching action movies##6
35. the chef is somewhere to the left of the person drinking cola##5
36. the person drinking cola is not to the right of the person drinking soy-milk##8
37. the social-worker is somewhere to the right of the person watching time-travel movies##5
38. the cottage house is not to the left of the dancer##8
39. the social-worker is not the person watching action movies##6
40. the person watching musical movies is on the left of the person watching action movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2     |   3    |    4     |       5        |       6       |       7       |
| Beverage      | milk   | cola     | tea    | 7up      | soy-milk       | fanta         | hot-chocolate |
| Job           | chef   | mechanic | dancer | musician | security-guard | social-worker | manager       |
| House   | cape-cod | ranch-style    | wooden    | cottage    | palace           | victorian         | art-deco          |
| Movie-Genre     | time-travel    | western     | musical   | action     | scientific     | sports          | adventure        |

