.:: Puzzle 4x7-Level-8-2::.
There 7 different types of food: artichoke, banana, cabbage, corn, lettuce, orange, plum
There are 7 different favourite beverages: iced-tea, cola, coffee, soy-milk, water, fanta, milk
The people perfer 7 different movie-genres: action, adventure, family, horror, mystery, romance, zombie
There are 7 different favourite colors: pink, grey, ebony, emerald, yellow, white, black
 1. the person drinking iced-tea is somewhere to the left of the person drinking milk##5
 2. the person watching family movies is on the left or right of the person watching horror movies##3
 3. the person drinking cola is the person who likes ebony##1
 4. the person drinking soy-milk is on the right of the person watching action movies##1
 5. the person who likes pink is not the person drinking iced-tea##6
 6. the person eating orange is somewhere between the person drinking iced-tea and the person who likes grey##7
 7. the person who likes grey is somewhere to the right of the person who likes pink##5
 8. the person eating corn is somewhere to the left of the person drinking water##5
 9. the person watching romance movies is somewhere to the left of the person watching mystery movies##5
10. the person watching adventure movies is somewhere to the left of the person drinking coffee##5
11. the person eating lettuce is not to the right of the person who likes pink##8
12. the person drinking soy-milk is somewhere to the left of the person drinking coffee##5
13. the person watching romance movies is somewhere between the person watching adventure movies and the person watching family movies##7
14. the person drinking fanta is not to the left of the person eating lettuce##8
15. the person who likes white is on the far right##1
16. the person eating orange is on the left or right of the person watching adventure movies##3
17. the person who likes black is on the left of the person eating artichoke##1
18. the person drinking fanta is on the left or right of the person eating cabbage##3
19. the person who likes emerald is on the left or right of the person watching family movies##3
20. the person watching mystery movies is on the left or right of the person watching romance movies##3
21. the person drinking iced-tea is somewhere to the right of the person drinking coffee##5
22. the person drinking fanta is not to the right of the person watching action movies##8
23. the person eating artichoke is somewhere between the person eating banana and the person watching family movies##7
24. the person watching horror movies is somewhere to the right of the person eating corn##5
25. the person watching romance movies is on the left or right of the person watching mystery movies##3
26. the person who likes grey is in an even position##4
27. the person who likes grey is not to the right of the person eating plum##8
28. the person eating corn is the person who likes black##1
29. the person watching horror movies is in an even position##4
30. the person eating cabbage is not to the right of the person drinking soy-milk##8
31. the person drinking fanta is on the left or right of the person drinking soy-milk##3
32. the person watching family movies is on the left or right of the person eating plum##3
33. the person eating cabbage is on the left of the person drinking coffee##1
34. the person who likes black is on the left of the person who likes ebony##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |      3       |     4      |     5     |     6     |     7      |
| Food          | lettuce  | cabbage   | orange       | plum       | corn      | artichoke | banana     |
| Beverage           | fanta | soy-milk    | coffee | iced-tea  | milk | cola     | water    |
| Movie-Genre   | action   | adventure | romance      | mystery    | family    | horror    | zombie     |
| Color     | pink | grey       | yellow    | emerald | black      | ebony       | white |

