There are 7 different favourite colors: grey, ebony, coral, aquamarine, azure, blue, fuchsia
The people prefer 7 different types of sport: rowing, skiing, rugby, basketball, water-polo, ice-hockey, snowboarding
 1. the person who's sport is rugby is on the left or right of the person drinking iced-tea##3
 2. the person drinking water is not to the left of the person eating carrot##8
 3. the person eating apricot is on the far right##1
 4. the person who likes grey is not to the right of the person who's sport is basketball##8
