11. the person drinking almond-milk is between the person eating potato and the person drinking iced-tea##2
12. the person who likes coral is not the person drinking water##6
13. the person drinking almond-milk is somewhere between the person who likes ebony and the person drinking iced-tea##7
14. the person eating apple is somewhere to the left of the person eating mango##5
15. the person drinking fanta is not to the right of the person who likes aquamarine##8
