17. the person who's sport is basketball is somewhere to the left of the person who likes aquamarine##5
18. the person who's sport is basketball is not to the right of the person drinking tea##8
19. the person who likes azure is not the person eating cabbage##6
20. the person drinking cola is not to the left of the person drinking tea##8
