27. the person who's sport is rugby is on the right of the person who's sport is snowboarding##1
28. the person eating cabbage is on the left or right of the person drinking tea##3
29. the person eating asparagus is on the right of the person who likes blue##1
30. the person drinking cola is somewhere between the person drinking soy-milk and the person who likes coral##7
31. the person eating potato is somewhere to the left of the person drinking fanta##5
