35. the person eating carrot is in an even position##4
36. the person who's sport is rugby is somewhere between the person who likes blue and the person drinking cola##7
37. the person who's sport is basketball is on the left or right of the person who likes grey##3
38. the person who's sport is water-polo is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is rowing##5

